    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/fe907db71d701a3a0d1df10e3af8a7fd.webp?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=49 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/3b5af29319b63d010eb8b6c3fcb96579.poster.avif?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/3b5af29319b63d010eb8b6c3fcb96579.webm?t=1761661683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>扮演一名年轻的旅馆老板，帮助你的巫婆祖母管理、装饰和扩展她那温馨的流动酒馆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/4bdd7cffe13dd5124d42a88b9e69ab30.webp?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=49 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/add1ac14cf2173db844880b8f563c0d8.poster.avif?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/add1ac14cf2173db844880b8f563c0d8.webm?t=1761661683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>应对光顾你酒馆的森林精灵和古老的波罗的海神灵的各种需求。管理员工，制作美味的菜单，让你的酒馆成为所有来访者的温馨港湾。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/50ac1f200b7e898a51b6d2a1a9594997.webp?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=49 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/bf3dc536e8a7c76737222b139b4592e0.poster.avif?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/bf3dc536e8a7c76737222b139b4592e0.webm?t=1761661683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>雇佣员工，管理财务，购买物资，精心维护你的酒馆。通过新增房间、设施和景点来扩展和升级酒馆，以吸引更多顾客并增加收入。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/090fd91469797a2e9d849cd08423a95c.webp?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/0b8673a7f5f4c520186ddb88a5fce8ad.poster.avif?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/0b8673a7f5f4c520186ddb88a5fce8ad.webm?t=1761661683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>通过各种装饰元素，包括家具、画作和地毯，个性化你的酒馆，创造一个温馨且独特的氛围。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/6131b9675a481d26676b90b34dfd10b2.webp?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/7ea2b440356c32c180b5bfa90cb76097.poster.avif?t=1761661683\" width=618 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009720/extras/7ea2b440356c32c180b5bfa90cb76097.webm?t=1761661683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>遇见受波罗的海民间传说启发的丰富多彩的角色，从淘气的女巫到飘渺的森林精灵和威严的异教神灵。",
